    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Wistrifunsus">Vuistrifuso</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Aricausus">Aricauso</name></persName> germani,
                        avitatoribus in loco <placeName ref="#places/165">Sexto</placeName>, filii
                            <persName>quondam Autelmi</persName>, donano pro anima <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3321" key="#Churches #Private_foundations"
                            >Sancti Miniati</orgName> sita in loco <placeName ref="#places/165"
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions #Wine #Oil #Fiscal_property #Mention #Churches #Private_foundations"
                            >Sexto</placeName>, pertinentes <rs key="#Domus #Mother_churches">domui
                            episcopatui</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Domus #Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName> istius <placeName ref="#places/4" key="#Cities"
                            >Lucensis</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Cities">civitatis</rs>, <rs key="#Private_foundations">qui est
                            fundata ipsa ecclesia Sancti Miniati a parentibus nostris</rs>: in
                        primis ibidem <rs key="#Salae">sala nostra</rs> illa ante ipsa ecclesia
                        Sancti Miniati, quod est da partibus trasmontante cum fundamento et edeficio
                        suo: et est tenente uno caput in <rs key="#Curtes">curte nostra</rs>, quas
                        nobis reservamus, alio caput tene in ipsa ecclesia, cum curticella et
                        pergula de partibus aquilonis, cum aliquantula terra post ipsa sala da
                        partibus meridie, qui lato tene in <rs key="#Wine #Fiscal_property #Mention"
                            >vinea domni regis</rs>, hec omnia in integrum; simul cum subdita illa,
                        qui est avembrata ad suprascripta ecclesia cum terra [ante] se da partibus
                        aquilonis, quomodo signa posite sunt; quidem et orto illo post ipsa
                        [ecclesia] da exurgente, cum <rs key="#Oil">aulives et arboribus suis</rs>
                        in integrum: lato uno tene in <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Mention">terra domni
                            regis</rs> et alio lato tene in <rs key="#Roads">via</rs>, quas a comune
                        reservamus, caput uno in <rs key="#Oil">oliveto</rs>, quas nobis reservamus,
                        quomodo signa posite sunt. Similiter offerimus in ipsa ecclesia vinea nostra
                        illa ubi dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Rivers #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Mention #Roads #Bridges/pontoons"
                            ref="#places/3334">ad <rs key="#Bridges/pontoons"
                        >Ponte</rs></placeName>, qui uno caput et uno lato tene in <rs key="#Roads"
                            >via publica</rs>, alio caput in <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Mention">terra domni
                            regis</rs>, et alio lato tene in <rs key="#Rivers">rivo Fisona</rs>, per
                        designatas locas in integrum; quidem et casa nostra illa in suprascripto
                        loco ubi dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Rivers #Landed_possessions #Mills #Fiscal_property #Mention #Roads"
                            ref="#places/3334">ad Panicale</placeName>; casa ipsa cum fundamento et
                        edeficio suo curte, orto, seo vinea et oliveto, totum insimul tenente ambo
                        capita in <rs key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Mention">terra
                            domni regis</rs>, lato uno tene in <rs key="#Roads">via</rs>, alio lato
                        tene in suprascripto <rs key="#Rivers">rivo Fisona</rs>; (…) una cum <rs
                            key="#Mills">molino</rs> illo quas infra ipse designate locas in
                        suprascripto rivo Fisona esse videtur, cum omne edeficio et conciatura sua
                        in integrum (…) Pena in duplum. <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name
                                ref="Teofridus">Teufridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive la cartula. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Mother_churches">Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness #Scabini"><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Scabini">scabino</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Ragibertus">Rachipertus</name></persName>
                        <persName>qd. <name ref="Radulus">Raduli</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName>
                        <persName>qd. <name ref="Teuprandus">Teoprandi</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Ardemannus">Ardimanno</name></persName>
                        <persName>qd. <name ref="Dulciprandus">Dulciprandi</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Medical_doctors"><name ref="Auripertus"
                                >Auripertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Medical_doctors">medicus</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Angelbertus">Angalpertus</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Ardemannus">Ardimannu</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Andreas">Andreas</name></persName>
                        et <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Aregis">Aroghis</name></persName>
                        <persName>qd. <name ref="Ghisi">Ghisi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Christianus"
                        >Cristianus</name></persName>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                <p>ChLA, 78, n. 19, pp. 56-59; MDL, 5/2, n. 597, pp. 358-359.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="additional">
                <p/>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="links">
                <p/>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Sottoscrizioni autografe: Vuistrifusu (autore), Auripertus medicus, Angalpertus,
                    Ardimannu, Cristianus, Teufridi notarius (scrittore). Sottoscrizioni con
                        <foreign>Signa</foreign>: Aricauso (autore), Petrus scabino, Rachipertus qd.
                    Raduli, Iohannes qd. Teoprandi, Ardimanno qd. Dulciprandi, Andreas et Aroghis
                    qd. Ghisi. Note tergali: al centro, in senso inverso rispetto al testo,
                    apparentemente di più mani di età tardomedievale e moderna le annotazioni che si
                    integrano: <foreign>Off(ersi)o in eccl(sie)a S(an)c(t)i Miniati de
                        Sesto</foreign>; Più a destra, forse del secolo XII ma depennato:
                        <foreign>Nescio [de q]uo</foreign>.</p>
            </div>
